TopicTitle: Video Wednesdays: DionDiBlank's on a Mission

Articles.Content:
<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/87dda5f22121633ebc5ff4dc817129a6/tumblr_inline_n6b9nhdFHb1rr2wit.jpg"/></p>

<p><iframe frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/2Zi-Dy6IHt8" width="420"></iframe></p>

<p><strong>DionDiBlank</strong> is on a mission. It’s the type of mission that might be old hat for some of you, but is definitely a big deal for a beginner. He plans to get into orbit, land without a parachute and do it in style. Will he make it? Will he prevail? Watch to find out.</p>
This reminds me like "Twitch thursdays" except it isn't on twitch
This guy is good at commentating, and has some great potential!
Such a noob, but in a really great way. I loved it, it reminded me of my first day playing KSP. Hope to see moar of his videos!
